divs: Sighting DetailsI was looking out the kitchen window and saw an object come down into the yard near my husband and son as they were working in the yard. I don't remember much else about the events that took place, but after many years, I was finally able to get my husband and son (both deceased) to tell me what happened to them.

Summary: Watched an object come down through a kitchen window.
